1
00:01:40,620 --> 00:01:45,720
[Love in Pavilion]

2
00:01:46,370 --> 00:01:50,830
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:53,330 --> 00:01:55,720
[Beast Kingdom]

4
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:04,100
[Herb Clinic]

5
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,790
Ladies,

6
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,310
I've found a courtyard for you.

7
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:07,200
Please have a seat for now.

8
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,060
I'll take you there immediately.

9
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:17,900
I didn't expect Miss Dongfang to come to the Beast Kingdom as well.

10
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,430
Did you tell her

11
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:21,800
you came here to investigate the Black Fox?

12
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,400
She probably figured it out.

13
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:27,800
But the key issue is that

14
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,800
the first clue I found

15
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,630
is related to Miss Dongfang's mother,

16
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:32,590
Jiang Juanxue.

17
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:35,880
She's the Saintess of the Northern Hill Sect,

18
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:40,210
and the Northern Hill Sect is closely connected to the origin of the Black Fox.

19
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:46,210
[Yajing Mansion]

20
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,750
This is the courtyard I picked out

21
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,280
based on your preferences.

22
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:56,829
It looks a little plain,

23
00:02:56,829 --> 00:02:59,120
but it's in a great location—quiet and elegant.

24
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,250
Thank you very much.

25
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:07,030
As for the person you're looking for,

26
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:08,680
things are a bit complicated.

27
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,590
Please be careful.

28
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,960
I'll take my leave then.

29
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,079
Huaizhu.

30
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,590
I quite like it here.

31
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,280
It's not bad.

32
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,710
But I really didn't expect to run into

33
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:27,370
Young Master Wangquan here in Beast Kingdom.

34
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,120
They just saved us.

35
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,710
I know.

36
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:33,150
That's why I thanked them.

37
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,610
And I didn't really make fun of them, did I?

38
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:39,960
Qinlan,

39
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,450
why have you never asked me

40
00:03:42,450 --> 00:03:44,380
why I brought you to Beast Kingdom?

41
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,520
Why should I ask?

42
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,800
Everything you do is right.

43
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:50,079
You trust me that much?

44
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,310
Of course.

45
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:53,750
You're one of a kind to me.

46
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,190
I'm going out for a walk,

47
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:59,390
to get familiar with the surroundings.

48
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:10,910
Erzhu Yu, the former owner of Drunken Dream Tower,

49
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:13,000
was assassinated a year ago.

50
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:16,680
The identity of the current leader remains unknown.

51
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,360
Jiang Juanxue once trained a woman,

52
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:26,000
named Erzhu Yu.

53
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:28,360
She was the owner of Drunken Dream Tower.

54
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,360
Was?

55
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,040
Yes.

56
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:32,630
She died mysteriously a year ago.

57
00:04:34,860 --> 00:04:36,070
After Erzhu Yu's death,

58
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:38,159
there should be something left in Drunken Dream Tower.

59
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:39,560
Who is the current owner?

60
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,800
The current owner of Drunken Dream Tower is very mysterious.

61
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,000
No one knows their identity.

62
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,720
I've already sent people to investigate.

63
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,600
We should have news soon.

64
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:49,320
But for now, the lead has gone cold,

65
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:51,950
and the Beast Kingdom has closed the city gates.

66
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:55,070
The current situation is quite unfavorable for us.

67
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:01,710
Who leaked the information to the ruler of Beast Kingdom?

68
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,370
Useless!

69
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,750
You've been in seclusion for three days

70
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,610
and haven't found a trace of them.

71
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:10,390
Could Wangquan Hongye really have grown wings and flown away?

72
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:13,520
Perhaps Jin Renfeng's information was false,

73
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,920
and Wangquan Hongye never came at all.

74
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:16,920
You fool!

75
00:05:18,070 --> 00:05:19,040
What good

76
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,570
would lying to me do him?

77
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,930
Tell Anayan to come and see me.

78
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:28,870
Yes.

79
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,060
Your Majesty.

80
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:33,680
There's no need to summon me.

81
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,860
[Anayan, National Preceptor of Beast Kingdom]

82
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,310
I'm already here.

83
00:05:40,770 --> 00:05:41,450
Good.

84
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,290
I went against all opposition

85
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:52,310
to make you the National Preceptor.

86
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,430
Why?

87
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,810
Because you personally told me

88
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:59,000
you would bring me Wangquan Hongye's head as repayment.

89
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:02,630
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

90
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:07,310
The assassins sent to kill Wangquan Hongye are already on their way.

91
00:06:07,490 --> 00:06:10,120
Then I'll wait and see.

92
00:06:33,690 --> 00:06:34,860
Make way, make way!

93
00:06:34,890 --> 00:06:35,590
Move!

94
00:06:35,610 --> 00:06:36,470
Move!

95
00:06:36,490 --> 00:06:37,230
Move!

96
00:06:40,180 --> 00:06:42,390
I'll go down and take a look. Wait for me here.

97
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:43,600
Someone reported that Ruyi Pavilion

98
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,000
is harboring members of the Yiqi Alliance!

99
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,750
Search!

100
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:47,430
Search every room!

101
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:48,240
Yes!

102
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,890
Young Master Wangquan,

103
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:56,980
Ms. Qingmu told me to take you out through the back door.

104
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:45,080
This sword is a fake after all.

105
00:07:46,130 --> 00:07:48,810
If that strike had been used for assassination,

106
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:50,270
no one in the entire Yiqi Alliance

107
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:52,159
would probably have been able to resist.

108
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:54,159
With such a master in Beast Kingdom,

109
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:57,159
didn't you receive any news, Yuan?

110
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,190
Yuan?

111
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:07,700
It's my negligence.

112
00:08:15,850 --> 00:08:17,200
It's not your fault.

113
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,920
Since my location has been exposed,

114
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,180
I can't stay in Ruyi Pavilion any longer.

115
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:24,920
Yuan, will you be in danger?

116
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,120
Don't worry.

117
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:29,990
I'll just say you're my important client.

118
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,510
Qingmu's has been doing business in Beast Kingdom

119
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:33,200
for many years.

120
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,780
We have some connections.

121
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,200
Quzhuo should be back soon.

122
00:08:39,370 --> 00:08:42,289
Just make two new identity tokens for us.

123
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,360
The identity tokens of the Beast Kingdom

124
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,080
are made from hematite.

125
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:48,790
And the mines are controlled by the ruler.

126
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:51,720
I barely managed to get two pieces,

127
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:54,020
and you've used them to save someone.

128
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,870
Yuan,

129
00:08:57,710 --> 00:08:58,770
you must have a way.

130
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:01,200
There is a way.

131
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:05,970
In the Beast Kingdom, demons are the property of demon tamers.

132
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,860
They don't need identity tokens.

133
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:11,390
You want us to pose as demons?

134
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:15,200
If you want to continue investigating in the Beast Kingdom and stay low-key,

135
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,750
this is the only way left.

136
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:21,380
It won't be a problem for Quzhuo

137
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,920
to make a demon core.

138
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,700
But which of us is going to pose as a demon?

139
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,720
What do you think?

140
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,880
Dongfang Huaizhu,

141
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,670
you think you can escape?

142
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:55,290
I've long since become one with you.

143
00:09:55,910 --> 00:10:00,030
Right now, I'm just being temporarily suppressed.

144
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:34,690
If that strike had been used for assassination,

145
00:10:34,690 --> 00:10:35,750
no one in the entire Yiqi Alliance

146
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:38,010
would probably have been able to resist.

147
00:10:44,990 --> 00:10:46,170
Is it you?

148
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,390
You're injured.

149
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,750
It's pretty serious.

150
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:11,510
It's nothing.

151
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:15,910
Why do you live in such a rundown place?

152
00:11:17,970 --> 00:11:18,930
I'm used to it.

153
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,670
You're the esteemed Master of the Zhang family.

154
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:24,200
Why do you subject yourself to such hardship?

155
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,720
Where are you going?

156
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,120
To find something to eat.

157
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,080
Ran.

158
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,800
Wangquan Hongye is not dead.

159
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:40,710
I'll find another opportunity.

160
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,840
Don't call me by that name anymore.

161
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,910
Ran is already dead.

162
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:12,780
[Drunken Dream Tower]

163
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,940
Come in, please. Come in, please.

164
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,770
Please, come in.

165
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:13,890
Come in, please. Come in, please.

166
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:17,870
Why can they go in,

167
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:19,080
but we can't?

168
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:23,850
Ladies, you don't even know the rules of Drunken Dream Tower.

169
00:12:23,850 --> 00:12:25,520
Why do you want to join the commotion?

170
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,560
What do you mean?

171
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,330
What rules does Drunken Dream Tower have?

172
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:33,530
Without a demon, you're not qualified to participate in the Demon Fight.

173
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:36,210
What is Demon Fight?

174
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:40,030
This is the place where demon tamers bring demons to fight.

175
00:12:40,610 --> 00:12:41,700
It's good that you know.

176
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:44,960
[Drunken Dream Tower]

177
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:43,910
If you want to enter Drunken Dream Tower,

178
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,890
you must participate in the Demon Fight.

179
00:12:45,890 --> 00:12:47,620
Otherwise, there's no chance.

180
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:52,750
Let's go.

181
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:55,540
Bye.

182
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:59,440
[Drunken Dream Tower]

183
00:12:56,670 --> 00:12:57,940
Sirs.

184
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,810
Please come in, please come in.

185
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,080
It's alright, Huaizhu.

186
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,750
Tomorrow I'll catch two small demons,

187
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:06,210
and we'll be able to get in.

188
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:14,270
Where did these pastries come from?

189
00:13:25,710 --> 00:13:27,260
Miss Huaizhu, you're back.

190
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,510
Am I not a person?

191
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:30,840
Why didn't you greet me?

192
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:33,010
Hello, Master Qinlan!

193
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:34,360
Who's your master?

194
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,670
You're back.

195
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,530
The food will be ready soon.

196
00:13:40,730 --> 00:13:42,090
So, all in all,

197
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:44,400
you two are here to seek refuge with us?

198
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:47,120
Collaboration. It's called collaboration.

199
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,250
Watch your wording.

200
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:50,620
I don't want to collaborate with you.

201
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,080
Come on, how can you...

202
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,000
Qinlan.

203
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,360
So, you came here

204
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:03,410
to investigate the Black Fox, right?

205
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:06,650
Yes. But somehow our identities were exposed,

206
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:08,540
and our whereabouts were leaked.

207
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:11,380
Hongye even got attacked at Ruyi Pavilion.

208
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:12,440
Are you injured?

209
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:15,270
Don't worry, I'm fine.

210
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:19,960
Then stay here.

211
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:21,630
We can look out for each other.

212
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:22,510
Huaizhu,

213
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:24,320
this isn't just looking out for each other.

214
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:26,650
It's more like you're taking care of them.

215
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,390
You've hit the nail on the head.

216
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:30,000
We're here to take care of you.

217
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:30,750
Quzhuo.

218
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:36,200
Here's the thing. We found some clues,

219
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:37,870
which include...

220
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,830
information about your mother.

221
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:44,130
All of this might be related to Drunken Dream Tower.

222
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,960
There's more information on the way,

223
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,720
and Ruyi Pavilion will send it over bit by bit.

224
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,840
And Quzhuo and I

225
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:51,490
will continue to investigate further.

226
00:14:51,490 --> 00:14:53,360
You two? Investigate further?

227
00:14:53,410 --> 00:14:54,620
How?

228
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:57,030
With that half-baked demon disguise talisman

229
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:59,290
of yours that doesn't even last a minute?

230
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:02,840
No. We'll turn into real demons.

231
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,810
Why don't you try being a human first?

232
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:25,200
Then I'll stop pretending.

233
00:15:30,150 --> 00:15:32,240
Let me properly introduce myself.

234
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:35,510
I'm Li Quzhuo, the second son of the Li family from Peach Garden.

235
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:36,910
Sit down and get to the point.

236
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:37,910
Alright, Hongye.

237
00:15:40,510 --> 00:15:41,770
I can make demon cores.

238
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:42,910
Demon cores?

239
00:15:44,380 --> 00:15:46,150
Quzhuo can make demon cores?

240
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,030
That's impressive.

241
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:47,910
Of course.

242
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,790
Once Qingmu Yuan sends over the demon king's blood,

243
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:50,740
I'll be able to make them.

244
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:51,960
By then, when we take it,

245
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:52,750
we'll become demons.

246
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,680
After that, Mrs. Wangquan, you...

247
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,150
Miss Huaizhu.

248
00:16:03,850 --> 00:16:06,680
Miss Huaizhu, you'll see for yourself.

249
00:16:08,050 --> 00:16:10,870
Alright. But there's no bedroom left.

250
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:12,280
Where will you stay?

251
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:15,000
We can tidy up the wood shed

252
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:15,910
and stay there.

253
00:16:16,630 --> 00:16:17,360
You do it.

254
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:22,550
I...

255
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:24,660
Alright, I'll do it.

256
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:34,750
Beast Kingdom has been conducting strict inspections lately.

257
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:36,690
I only managed to get these two bottles of demon blood.

258
00:16:36,690 --> 00:16:38,200
One is from a snake demon,

259
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,000
and the other is from a dog demon.

260
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,120
Hongye,

261
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:44,630
do you know the consequences of consuming

262
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:46,490
the heart's blood of a demon king?

263
00:16:46,510 --> 00:16:48,240
With Quzhuo here, don't worry.

264
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,390
I'll use the gourd to strip away the demon's influence,

265
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:52,030
and there won't be any problems.

266
00:16:52,030 --> 00:16:53,760
It's not as simple as you think.

267
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:55,740
Once you consume demon blood,

268
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:57,150
you'll lose the ability to use magic power

269
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:58,700
and can only use demonic power.

270
00:16:58,700 --> 00:17:01,400
Additionally, your behavior will be influenced by the demon nature,

271
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:04,010
which could become your fatal weakness.

272
00:17:04,390 --> 00:17:05,819
Especially snake demons.

273
00:17:05,819 --> 00:17:07,720
Their biggest weakness is their extreme fear of cold.

274
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,720
In this desert area,

275
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:11,680
once night falls, they'll become especially vulnerable.

276
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,550
The demon nature will be gone in ten days.

277
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:14,920
Yuan, you don't have to worry.

